Experimental improvement of the Polopoly eclipse plugin.

Use Ctrl+Alt+I to open input template by externalid (Open Input Template)
Use Ctrl+Alt+P to open content by externalid (Open Content by External Id)
Use Ctrl+Alt+E to open (input template|content) by externalid (Open by External Id)
Use Alt+Shift+X I to import currently active file as content XML (Command name Import Content XML)
